<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3154684" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="34">If the data of the source sheet has been changed, $[officename] recalculates the DataPilot table. To recalculate the tables, choose <emph>Data - DataPilot - Refresh</emph>. Do the same after you have imported an Excel Pivot table into $[officename] Calc.</paragraph>
